Package: epaclades
Title: Classification of Phylogenetic Placements to Clades
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
   person("Ondrej", "Mikula", , "onmikula@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4361-0581"))
Description: The package combines results of phylogenetic placement analysis performed in RAxML's EPA or in pplacer with information about partitioning of the tree into significant clades (species, lineages...) For each query sequence it outputs the probability of belonging to the defined clades.
License: `use_mit_license()`
